Beate Uhse Posts Full-Year Loss of $84 Million as Sales Decline

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-04-28T16:21:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/beate-uhse-posts-full-year-loss-of-84-million-as-sales-decline.html
Beate Uhse AG (USE)  said today it will
post an operating loss of 56.5 million euros ($84 million) for
2010 as sales fell 14 percent to 197.7 million euros.  The company said in a statement that it will postpone the
publication of its financial statements announced for today to
May 19.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Richard Weiss in  Frankfurt  at 
 rweiss5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net . 